spec_data.Name: pyrasite
spec_data.Description:
Pyrasite uses the GNU debugger to inject code into a running Python process.
It is comprised of a command-line tool, and a Python API. This package
also comes with a variety of example payloads.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 26 Feb 2017 03:22:21 PM EST, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Code injection and monitoring of running Python processes
